From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Mike <michaelgorney4@gmail.com>
Date: Tue, 9 Jun 2026 21:53:39 -0400
Subject: [PATCH 47/59] Remove "implements" from type-expressions

Removed Implements from CXXMGTypeExprOpcode.
Removed type-expression predicate parsing from ParseCXXMGTypeExpr.cpp and its probes from ParseExpr.cpp.
Removed type-expression predicate Sema APIs/evaluation from SemaCXXMGTypeExpr.cpp / Sema.h.
Removed the stale parser declaration.
Deleted type-expression tests that were really trait implements tests.
Trimmed the mixed type-expression test so it no longer references implements.
Kept implements handling in the trait path.

